headline: Stanley Black & Decker Announces Release Date for First Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: Stanley Black & Decker (NYSE: SWK) will broadcast its first quarter 2025 earnings webcast on Wednesday, April 30, 2025. The webcast will begin at 8:00AM ET.

headline: 3 Reasons to Sell SWK and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Shareholders of Stanley Black & Decker would probably like to forget the past six months even happened. The stock dropped 28.7% and now trades at $78.23. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
